由[[伊達勇登|伊達勇登]]導演、[[Studio_Pierrot|Studio Pierrot]]和[[東京電視台|東京電視台]]製作的火影忍者動漫於2002年10月3日在日本首播，並在播出220集後於2007年2月8日完結。<ref name="tvtokyo">{{cite web|url=http://www.tv-tokyo.co.jp/anime/naruto2002/story_f.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160822094056/http://www.tv-tokyo.co.jp/anime/naruto2002/story_f.html |archive-date=2016-08-22 |title=Naruto story |publisher=[[TV_Tokyo|TV Tokyo]] |language=ja|url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tv-tokyo.co.jp/anime/naruto2002/stuff_f.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160702164537/http://www.tv-tokyo.co.jp/anime/naruto2002/stuff_f.html |archive-date=2016-07-02 |title=Naruto staff |publisher=[[TV_Tokyo|TV Tokyo]] |language=ja|url-status=dead }}</ref>其中135集改編自漫畫第一部分；剩下85集為動畫原創劇情。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animesays.com/list/naruto/ |title=Naruto Filler & Episode List – AnimeSays |publisher=AnimeSays |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160220180640/http://www.animesays.com/list/naruto/ |archive-date=2016-02-20|url-status=dead}}</ref>當漫畫改編成動畫系列時，[[西尾鐵也|西尾鐵也]]也是火影忍者的角色設計師；[[岸本齊史|岸本齊史]]曾要求[[西尾鐵也|西尾鐵也]]擔任這個職位。<ref>{{cite book|title=Manga's Cultural Crossroads|last=Gan|first=Sheuo Hui|date=2013|publisher=[[Taylor_and_Francis|Taylor and Francis]]|isbn=978-1-134-10283-9|location=Hoboken|page=227|chapter=Auteur and Anime as Seen in the Naruto TV Series|editor1-last=Berndt|editor1-first=Jacqueline|editor2-last=Kümmerling-Meibauer|editor2-first=Bettina}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2012-07-21/kishimoto/naruto-manga-to-continue-longer-than-1.5-years |title=Kishimoto: Naruto Manga to Continue Longer Than 1.5 Years |work=Anime News Network|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170110231938/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2012-07-21/kishimoto/naruto-manga-to-continue-longer-than-1.5-years |archive-date=2017-01-10 |url-status=live}}</ref>從 2009 年4月29日開始，最初的火影忍者動畫開始在週三和週四重播（直到2009年9月的第四週改為僅週三）。該系列的劇集已在VHS和DVD上發行，並收集盒裝形式。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tv-tokyo.co.jp/anime/naruto2002/goods/dvd_01.html#01 |publisher=TV Tokyo |title=Naruto ナルト－ 巻ノ一 |trans-title=Naruto {{endash}} Volume No.1 |language=ja |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5hjHlmuLN?url=http://www.tv-tokyo.co.jp/anime/naruto2002/goods/dvd_01.html |archive-date=2009-06-22 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tv-tokyo.co.jp/anime/naruto2002/goods/dvd_05.html#2 |publisher=[[TV_Tokyo|TV Tokyo]] |title=Naruto 5th Stage |language=ja|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081013080609/http://www.tv-tokyo.co.jp/anime/naruto2002/goods/dvd_05.html |archive-date=2008-10-13 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/B001FX7914 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160427191219/http://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/B001FX7914 |archive-date=2016-04-27 |title=Naruto-ナルト- DVD-BOX I 参上!うずまきナルト |trans-title=Naruto {{endash}} DVD {{endash}} BOX I Rising! Naruto Uzumaki |language=ja|url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/B001FX790U |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160321155345/http://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/B001FX790U |archive-date=2016-03-21 |title=Naruto-ナルト- DVD-BOX III 激突!ナルトVSサスケ |trans-title=Naruto DVD Box III Crash! Naruto VS Sasuke |language=ja|url-status=dead }}</ref>

[[碧日|VIZ Media]]授權動畫系列在[[DVD區域碼#區域碼|區域1]]市場播放和發行。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2009-03-23/viz-confirms-plans-to-present-new-dubbed-naruto|title=Viz Confirms Plans to Present New Dubbed Naruto|date=2009-03-23|work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161114142722/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2009-03-23/viz-confirms-plans-to-present-new-dubbed-naruto|archive-date=2016-11-14|url-status=live}}</ref>該動畫的英文配音於2005年9月10日開始播出，並於2009年1月31日結束，共有209集在美國[[卡通頻道|Cartoon Network]]的[[Toonami|Toonami]]播出。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2005-08-11/naruto-on-cartoon-network|title=Naruto on Cartoon Network|date=2005-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101029151758/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2005-08-11/naruto-on-cartoon-network|archive-date=2010-10-29|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="EnglishSeason1">{{cite news|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2009-12-02/1st-naruto-anime-finale-premieres-on-canada-ytv|title=1st Naruto Anime's Finale Premieres on Canada's YTV|date=2009-12-02|work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161114211617/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2009-12-02/1st-naruto-anime-finale-premieres-on-canada-ytv|archive-date=2016-11-14|url-status=live}}</ref>這些劇集還在[[讀賣電視台|讀賣電視台]]的 {{tsl|en|Bionix}}（加拿大）<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2005-08-09/naruto-delayed-on-ytv|title=Naruto Delayed on YTV|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|date=2005-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160910060641/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2005-08-09/naruto-delayed-on-ytv|archive-date=2016-09-10|url-status=live}}</ref>、{{tsl|en|Disney XD (British and Irish TV channel)|Jetix}}（英國）<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2006-05-23/naruto-uk-plans-revealed|title=Naruto UK Plans Revealed|date=2006-05-23|work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160910064031/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2006-05-23/naruto-uk-plans-revealed|archive-date=2016-09-10|url-status=live}}</ref>和{{tsl|en|SABC 2}}（南非）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sabc2.co.za/sabc/home/sabc2/shows/details?id=549c43df-ff0a-4dab-af24-8eff695586be&title=Naruto|title=Naruto|website=SABC 2|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216175947/http://www.sabc2.co.za/sabc/home/sabc2/shows/details?id=549c43df-ff0a-4dab-af24-8eff695586be&title=Naruto|archive-date=2017-02-16|url-status=dead}}</ref>的節目上播出，並於 2006 年 3 月 28 日以 DVD 形式發行。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B000CEXG3W |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160116221853/http://www.amazon.com/dp/B000CEXG3W |archive-date=2016-01-16 |publisher=[[Viz_Media|Viz Media]] |title=Naruto, Vol. 1 (DVD)|url-status=dead }}</ref>2017年8月25日，[[Starz_(電視頻道)|Starz]]宣布他們將從 2017年9月1日開始為其[[隨選視訊|隨選視訊]]服務提供該系列劇集。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/882819-starz-app-september-2017-movies-and-tv-titles-announced|title=Starz app September 2017 Movies and TV Titles Announced|date=2017-08-25|publisher=ComingSoon.net|archive-date=2018-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180724044655/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/882819-starz-app-september-2017-movies-and-tv-titles-announced|url-status=live}}</ref>未刪減版以DVD套裝形式發行，每套包含12-15集，並根據故事情節有些微調整。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B002HW5G2Q |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160413040619/http://www.amazon.com/dp/B002HW5G2Q |archive-date=2016-04-13 |publisher=[[Viz_Media|Viz Media]] |title=Naruto Uncut, Vol. 1 (DVD Box Set)|url-status=dead }}</ref>在美國播出中，有時會對酒精、[[日本文化|日本文化]]、性暗示以及血腥和死亡橋段進行審查，但仍保留在DVD版本中。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2007/11/10/naruto-readers-guide?page=2 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160130193937/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/11/10/naruto-readers-guide?page=2 |archive-date=2016-01-30 |author=Sparrow, A.E. |title=Naruto Reader's Guide |website=[[IGN|IGN]]|url-status=dead |date=2007-11-09 }}</ref>被審查的場景之一是[[鳴人|鳴人]]和[[宇智波佐助|佐助]]的意外接吻，符合刪除暗示同性戀關係內容的長期趨勢。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://cbldf.org/2019/03/anime-censorship-in-the-early-2000s/|title=Anime Censorship in the 90s and Early 2000s {{!}} Comic Book Legal Defense Fund|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191204200236/http://cbldf.org/2019/03/anime-censorship-in-the-early-2000s/|url-status=live}}</ref>其它頻道剪掉了更多內容，例如{{tsl|en|Disney XD (British and Irish TV channel)|Jetix}}刪除了帶有血腥、不雅語言和吸煙的場景。該系列還授權給 [[Hulu|Hulu]]、[[Joost|Joost]]和[[Crunchyroll|Crunchyroll]]的許可，讓它們在網路上播出，並附有原始日文配音及英文字幕。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-09-23/joost-streams-legal-subbed-naruto-death-note-for-free |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161204201849/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-09-23/joost-streams-legal-subbed-naruto-death-note-for-free |archive-date=2016-12-04 |date=2008-09-23 |title=Joost Streams Legal, Subbed Naruto, Death Note for Free (Updated) |work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-09-23/hulu-website-launches-channel-for-free-legal-anime |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161203190930/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-09-23/hulu-website-launches-channel-for-free-legal-anime |archive-date=2016-12-03 |date=2008-09-23 |work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] |title=Hulu.com Launches Channel for Free, Legal Anime Streams (Update 2)|url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-11-17/tv-tokyo-to-also-stream-naruto-through-crunchyroll |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161106103242/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-11-17/tv-tokyo-to-also-stream-naruto-through-crunchyroll |archive-date=2016-11-06 |title=TV Tokyo to Also Stream Naruto Through Crunchroll |work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] |date=2008-11-11 |url-status=dead }}</ref>2017年6月1日，宣布原版火影忍者電視動畫系列的HD重製版將於6月24日在日本電視上首播，從該劇的第一集開始。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-06-01/scenario-art-performs-new-ending-theme-for-boruto-naruto-next-generations-anime/.116877 |title=Scenario Art Performs New Ending Theme For Boruto: Naruto Next Generations Anime |date=2017-06-01 |website=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170606104125/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-06-01/scenario-art-performs-new-ending-theme-for-boruto-naruto-next-generations-anime/.116877 |archive-date=2017-06-06 |url-status=live}}</ref>

=====火影忍者疾風傳=====
{{main|火影忍者疾風傳}}
《火影忍者疾風傳》由[[Studio_Pierrot|Studio Pierrot]]開發，[[伊達勇登|伊達勇登]]導演，是原《火影忍者》動漫的續集，對應漫畫的第二部分。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tv-tokyo.co.jp/anime/naruto/staff/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170308114433/http://www.tv-tokyo.co.jp/anime/naruto/staff/ |archive-date=2017-03-08 |title=スタッフ•キャスト |trans-title=Naruto – Staff Cast |publisher=TV Tokyo|url-status=dead }}</ref>於2007年2月15日在東京電視台首播，並於2017年3月23日結束。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tv-tokyo.co.jp/anime/naruto/episodes2007.html |title=Naruto: Shippuden episodes from 2007 |language=ja |publisher=TV Tokyo |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090523041139/http://www.tv-tokyo.co.jp/anime/naruto/episodes2007.html |archive-date=2009-05-23 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-03-23/naruto-shippuden-anime-ending-on-500th-episode-confirmed/.113787 |title=Naruto Shippūden Anime's Ending on 500th Episode Confirmed |work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170323123510/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-03-23/naruto-shippuden-anime-ending-on-500th-episode-confirmed/.113787 |archive-date=2017-03-23 |url-status=live}}</ref>2009 年1月8日，東京電視台開始通過[[串流媒體|串流媒體]]向每月訂閱者播放新劇集；每集在日語版本發行後的一小時內都可以在線上觀看，並提供英文字幕。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tv-tokyo.co.jp/contents/ir/eng/press/pubfile/20081117.pdf |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111121103305/http://www.tv-tokyo.co.jp/contents/ir/eng/press/pubfile/20081117.pdf |archive-date=2011-11-21 |title=Press Release; Re: Animated Television Series Naruto available worldwide, same day as Japanese Premiere |publisher=TV Tokyo |date=2008-11-17 |url-status=dead }}</ref>

[[碧日|VIZ Media]]於2009年1月2日開始在其系列網站上播放英文字幕劇集，包括已發行的劇集及來自日本的新劇集。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2008-11-17/viz-media-announces-unprecedented-multimedia-campaign-to-provide-near-simultaneous-u.s-japan-release-of-new-naruto-shippuden-animated-episodes-for-free-on-www.naruto.com |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160415095735/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2008-11-17/viz-media-announces-unprecedented-multimedia-campaign-to-provide-near-simultaneous-u.s-japan-release-of-new-naruto-shippuden-animated-episodes-for-free-on-www.naruto.com |archive-date=2016-04-15 |title=Viz Media Announces Unprecedented Multimedia Campaign to Provide Near Simultaneous U.S.-Japan Release of New Naruto Shippuden Animated Episodes for Free on www.Naruto.com |work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] |date=2008-11-17|url-status=dead }}</ref>在美國，《火影忍者疾風傳》的英文配音從2009年10月28日起每週在[[迪士尼XD|迪士尼XD]]上播出，直到2011年11月5日第98集。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.toonzone.net/schedule/displaySeries.php?seriesID=327&networkID=17|title=Naruto Shippuden Disney XD schedule|date=2009-12-11|publisher=toonzone.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120319194657/http://www.toonzone.net/schedule/displaySeries.php?seriesID=327&networkID=17|archive-date=2012-03-19|url-status=dead}}</ref>第99至338集在[[網路電視|網路電視]]{{tsl|en|Neon Alley}}上首播，直到2016年5月4日關閉。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2014-04-01/viz-media-neon-alley-begins-a-new-era-for-digital-anime-and-delivers-the-best-in-free-dynamic-programming|title=VIZ Media's Neon Alley Begins a New Era for Digital Anime and Delivers the Best in Free Dynamic Programming|date=2014-04-01|work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161119172817/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2014-04-01/viz-media-neon-alley-begins-a-new-era-for-digital-anime-and-delivers-the-best-in-free-dynamic-programming|archive-date=2016-11-19|url-status=live}}</ref>該動畫從2014年1月5日起在[[Adult_Swim|Adult Swim]]的[[Toonami|Toonami]]開始每週播出。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2014-01-03/naruto-shippuden-debuts-on-adult-swim-toonami-this-sunday-at-12-30am|title=Naruto Shippuden Debuts on Adult Swim's Toonami This Sunday 1/5 at 12:30AM|date=2014-01-03|work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140208030816/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2014-01-03/naruto-shippuden-debuts-on-adult-swim-toonami-this-sunday-at-12-30am|archive-date=2014-02-08|url-status=live}}</ref>

該系列在日本以[[DVD區域碼#區域碼|區域2]]DVD發行，每片光碟有四到五集；DVD發行四個系列，並按故事情節劃分。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/B0053F1BPK |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306025848/http://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/B0053F1BPK |archive-date=2016-03-06 |title=Naruto-ナルト- 疾風伝 五影集結の章 1 DVD |trans-title=Naruto {{endash}} Shippuden Shinjo Congregation Chapter 1 DVD |language=ja|url-status=dead }}</ref>第七部《火影忍者疾風傳》合輯 DVD 中包含了[[原創動畫錄影帶|OVA]]《疾風！木葉學園傳》。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.tv-tokyo.co.jp/anime/naruto/goods/dvd_6th.html |title=Naruto-ナルト- 疾風伝 風影奪還の章7 |publisher=TV Tokyo |language=ja |trans-title=Naruto {{endash}} Shippuden Windscape Retreat Chapter 7 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080104052441/http://www.tv-tokyo.co.jp/anime/naruto/goods/dvd_6th.html |archive-date=2008-01-04 |url-status=dead}}</ref>《[[卡卡西外傳～戰場上的少年時代～|卡卡西外傳～戰場上的少年時代～]]》於2009年12月16日發布，故事圍繞著[[旗木卡卡西|旗木卡卡西]]的童年展開。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cdjapan.co.jp/product/ANZB-3381 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150721180812/http://www.cdjapan.co.jp/product/ANZB-3381 |archive-date=2015-07-21 |title=Naruto Shippuden Kakashi Gaiden {{endash}} Senjo no Boys' Life w/ CD, Limited Edition |publisher=CDJapan|url-status=dead }}</ref>

該系列的第一張北美DVD於2009年9月29日發行。<ref name="Region1 dvds announced">{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B001RIZ8WE |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307185526/http://www.amazon.com/dp/B001RIZ8WE |archive-date=2016-03-07 |title=Naruto Shippuden, Vol. 1 |url-status=dead }}</ref>從2010年1月26日的第一季開始，後續劇集作為DVD盒裝的一部分發行。<ref name="Naruto Shippuden Box Set 1">{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B002S4DOA4 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160222110237/http://www.amazon.com/dp/B002S4DOA4 |archive-date=2016-02-22 |title=Naruto Shippuden, Box Set 1 (DVD) |publisher=[[Viz_Media|Viz Media]]|url-status=dead }}</ref>在英國，該系列由{{tsl|en|Manga Entertainment}}授權，於2010年6月14日發行了第一部DVD。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B0037B2WSC |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160324103003/http://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B0037B2WSC |archive-date=2016-03-24 |title=Naruto Shippuden Box Set 1 DVD |url-status=dead |date=2010-06-14 }}</ref>

