cdjapan.co.jp/product/SVWC-7568 |archive-date=2016-01-24 |title=Movie Naruto Shippuden Kizuna Original Soundtrack |publisher=CDJapan|url-status=dead}}</ref>該系列的最後一部原聲帶預計於 2017年末發行，由[[Aniplex|Aniplex]]針對收錄曲目進行民調。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aniplex.co.jp/naruto/FINALBEST/|title=Naruto Final Best|publisher=[[Aniplex|Aniplex]]|language=ja|archive-date=2017-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904203057/http://www.aniplex.co.jp/naruto/FINALBEST/|url-status=live}}</ref>

