== 評價 ==
===漫畫===
幾位評論家針對戰鬥橋段與情節發展間的平衡進行評價；[[IGN|IGN]]的AE Sparrow和[[Anime_News_Network|動漫新聞網(ANN)]]的Casey Brienza認為平衡結果就是一個強大的故事情節，<ref name="ANNManga28Review">{{cite news|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/naruto/gn-28|title=Naruto GN 28 Review|date=2008-08-07|work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161116001305/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/naruto/gn-28|archive-date=2016-11-16|author=Brienza, Casey|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2007/02/28/naruto-vol-13-review|title=Naruto Vol. 13 Review|date=2007-02-27|website=[[IGN|IGN]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160115183335/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/02/28/naruto-vol-13-review|archive-date=2016-01-15|author=Sparrow, A. E.|url-status=dead}}</ref>但同樣為[[Anime_News_Network|ANN]]撰稿的Carl Kimlinger表示戰鬥太多，這減緩了劇情節奏。<ref name="ANNManga8-10Review">{{cite news|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/naruto-gn-8-10|title=Naruto GN 8–10 {{endash}} Review|date=2006-11-02|work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160510144105/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/naruto-gn-8-10|archive-date=2016-05-10|author=Kimlinger, Carl|url-status=dead}}</ref>Kimlinger喜歡角色設計，並認可戰鬥場景的設計<ref name="ANNManga8-10Review" />，這也引起了Rik Spanjers的積極評價，他認為場景的刺激源自岸本描繪動作的技巧。<ref name="ANNManga8-10Review" />為{{tsl|en|Twisted Manga}}撰稿的Garvita Gaur 表示同意，將這部作品描述為「戲劇性的、令人興奮的，且正好適合他來講述的故事」。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twistedmanga.com/naruto-volume-14-recap-and-review|title=Naruto v. 14 Review|publisher=TwistedManga.com|author=Lugo, Javier|url-status=live}}</ref>

動漫與漫畫雜誌{{tsl|en|Neo (magazine)|Neo}}將火影忍者的角色描述為“令人厭煩”，但認為該系列“幾乎令人作嘔的上癮”正是由於其人物塑造的品質，<ref name="neo023">{{Cite news|title=Naruto Vol. 1: Unleashed|last=White|first=Nik|date=September 2006|publisher=Uncooked Media|issue=23|pages=70–71|issn=1744-9596|magazine=[[Neo_(magazine)|Neo]]|place=United Kingdom}}</ref>並且在Briana Lawrence看來，角色的成長給了第二部分成人的感覺。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mania.com/naruto-vol28_article_83777.html|title=Naruto Vol.#28 review|date=2008-03-27|publisher=Mania Entertainment|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110810231741/http://www.mania.com/naruto-vol28_article_83777.html|archive-date=2011-08-10|author=Lawrence, Briana|url-status=dead}}</ref>在對單行本第28冊的評論中，Brienza還稱讚了第二部分的故事情節和人物塑造，儘管她評價道並非每一冊都達到高品質。<ref name="ANNManga28Review" />

第二部分的戰鬥橋段獲得讚譽，最著名的就是[[鳴人|鳴人]]和[[宇智波佐助|佐助]]的戰鬥，導致他們的角色發展產生重大變化。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://activeanime.com/html/2009/01/18/naruto-vol-33/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160317091949/http://activeanime.com/html/2009/01/18/naruto-vol-33/ |archive-date=2016-03-17 |title=Naruto Vol. 33 |publisher=Active Anime |author=Jones, Davey C. |date=2008-01-18 |url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mangalife.com/features/MangaLifeSpotlightonNaruto.htm|title=MangaLife Spotlight on: Naruto v34-v40!|website=Manga Life|last=Cooper|first=Park|date=2009-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090326001417/http://www.mangalife.com/features/MangaLifeSpotlightonNaruto.htm|archive-date=2009-03-26|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/naruto/gn-42|title=Naruto GN 42-44|author=Brienza, Casey|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|date=2009-04-25|archive-date=2009-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090426044213/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/naruto/gn-42|url-status=live}}</ref>同時，這兩位忍者的最終決戰，因其動作編排、藝術性以及決戰後展現出兩人個性的深度而獲得極大讚譽。一些評論家批評[[火影忍者角色列表#大筒木一族|大筒木輝夜]]是最沒娛樂性的反派，因此[[鳴人|鳴人]]和[[宇智波佐助|佐助]]的對決就更具吸引力。結局獲得了[[動畫新聞網|ANN]]和Comic Book Bin的近乎滿分評價，後者還稱讚主角的名氣。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/naruto/gn-72/.93358|title=Naruto GN 72|website=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|date=2015-10-04|last=McNulty|first=Amy|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170711082141/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/naruto/gn-72/.93358|archive-date=2017-07-11}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comicbookbin.com/naruto071.html|title=Naruto: Volume 72 manga review|website=Comic Book Bin|date=2015-10-04|author=Douresseaux, Leroy|archive-date=2020-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200605170324/http://www.comicbookbin.com/naruto071.html|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/house-of-1000-manga/2014-11-13/naruto-part-ii/.80991|title=House of 1000 Manga Naruto Part II|last=Thompson|first=Jason|date=2014-11-13|website=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170428143850/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/house-of-1000-manga/2014-11-13/naruto-part-ii/.80991|archive-date=2017-04-28|author-link=Jason Thompson (writer)}}</ref>

[[東京工藝大學|東京工藝大學]]漫畫系教授伊藤剛將該系列的發展與《[[七龍珠|七龍珠]]》對照，稱兩部漫畫對三維動作的描繪很好地呈現武打動作。伊藤剛認為讀者可以通過角色戰鬥時的內心獨白對他們產生同理心。<ref>{{Cite book|author-last=Itō |author-first=Gō |chapter=Particularities of boys' manga in the early 21st century: How NARUTO differs from DRAGON BALL |pages=9–16 |chapter-url=http://imrc.jp/images/upload/lecture/data/web_version_cologne%E8%AB%96%E9%9B%86.pdf |title=Intercultural crossovers, transcultural flows manga/comics |editor-last=Berndt |editor-first=Jacqueline |year= 2012 |series=Global Manga Studies |volume=2 |publisher=Kyoto Seika University International Manga Research Center |isbn=978-4-905187-06-6 |oclc=962747377 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303205554/http://imrc.jp/images/upload/lecture/data/Web_Version_Cologne%E8%AB%96%E9%9B%86.pdf |archive-date=2016-03-03 }}</ref>

該系列還影響了電影《[[歪小子史考特|歪小子史考特]]》；導演[[艾德格·萊特|艾德格·萊特]]說他的靈感來自漫畫中每當出現「必殺技」時，必定伴隨潛在副作用。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cracked.com/pictofacts-761-12-unexpected-inspirations-behind-famous-movies-shows/|title=12 Strange Origin Stories Behind Famous Movies And Shows|publisher=Cracked|date=2017-09-02|archive-date=2019-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191230125831/https://www.cracked.com/pictofacts-761-12-unexpected-inspirations-behind-famous-movies-shows/|url-status=live}}</ref>當漫畫結束時，多位作者對岸本的成就表示祝賀。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2014-11-08/shonen-jump-manga-creators-also-send-off-naruto-with-comments/.80813|title=Shonen Jump Manga Creators Also Send Off Naruto With Comments|work=Anime News Network|date=2014-11-08|archive-date=2017-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171020140908/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2014-11-08/shonen-jump-manga-creators-also-send-off-naruto-with-comments/.80813|url-status=live}}</ref>總體而言，戰鬥場景因其優秀設計而贏得讚譽，遊戲開發商[[CyberConnect2|CyberConnect2]]在開發火影忍者遊戲時有考慮到這一點。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://es.ign.com/naruto-1/86392/feature/los-20-mejores-duelos-de-naruto-y-naruto-shippuden?p=2|title=Los 20 mejores duelos de Naruto y Naruto Shippuden|publisher=IGN|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180314154416/http://es.ign.com/naruto-1/86392/feature/los-20-mejores-duelos-de-naruto-y-naruto-shippuden?p=2|archive-date=2018-03-14|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://es.ign.com/naruto-1/86392/feature/los-20-mejores-duelos-de-naruto-y-naruto-shippuden?p=4|title=Los 20 mejores duelos de Naruto y Naruto Shippuden|publisher=IGN|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180407170501/http://es.ign.com/naruto-1/86392/feature/los-20-mejores-duelos-de-naruto-y-naruto-shippuden?p=4|archive-date=2018-04-07|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="fukuoka">{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CNPRz5MOiCY|title=Naruto Shippuden Ultimate Ninja Storm 2 - PS3 / X360 - Behind the Game 2: Ninja Art|publisher=Youtube|work=Bandai Namco Entertainment Europe|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170926144154/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CNPRz5MOiCY|archive-date=2017-09-26}}</ref><ref name="stormtwo">{{cite web|url=https://venturebeat.com/2010/10/16/9-questions-for-naruto-shippuden-ultimate-ninja-storm-2s-hiroshi-matsuyama/|title=9 Questions for Naruto Shippuden: Ultimate Ninja Storm 2's Hiroshi Matsuyama|date=2010-10-16|publisher=Venture Beat|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161003033937/http://venturebeat.com/2010/10/16/9-questions-for-naruto-shippuden-ultimate-ninja-storm-2s-hiroshi-matsuyama/|archive-date=2016-10-03}}</ref>

